
# Setup (requires admin once)
1. Create udev rule as root:

sudo nano /etc/udev/rules.d/99-em90.rules

Add:

SUBSYSTEM=="hidraw", ATTRS{idVendor}=="28e9", ATTRS{idProduct}=="028a", GROUP="plugdev", MODE="0660"

2. Reload rules and replug device:

sudo udevadm control --reload-rules
sudo udevadm trigger

3. Add your user to plugdev:

sudo usermod -aG plugdev $USER
